# LucidGate example list: substitutionlist
# Format: One literal streaming substitution per line: search => replacement. Empty replacement deletes the matched text.
# Lines beginning with # are comments and are ignored by the loader.
# To activate a rule, copy one example, remove the leading # and adapt it to your environment.
# You can include another file with: .Include<relative-or-absolute-path>
#
# Commented examples:
# http://example.test => https://example.test
# internal codename => [redacted]
# staging-password => [redacted]
# debug=true => debug=false
# X-Unsafe => X-Safe
# old.example.test => new.example.test
# api_key=demo => api_key=[redacted]
# token=demo => token=[redacted]
# private note => public note
# legacy path => current path
